latestIgtvVideos.title: #ZeroTouchFacial with @cherylsskincare
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
My skin needed some pampering and excess screen time made it really dull during this lockdown. After months of being home I stepped out to get my glow back at @salonhaircrush for a #ZeroTouchFacial by @Cherylsskincare . ❤️❤️ I was relieved seeing how careful they were with their safety and hygiene measures. There were different facial options for every skin time and I got the #SensiGlow facial to help sooth the redness on my face. 
🧖🏼‍♀️ 💆🏼‍♀️

latestIgtvVideos.title: Sunday Organic Hair and Skin Care Routine✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption: I came across this brand @thetribeconcepts and bought a bunch of products from their website and I’m absolutely in love with them. 🧖🏼‍♀️ As we are switching to chemical free ways of living life and shifting to environment friendly stuff and ofcourse supporting local brands I wanted to try an entire routine with one brand. 🌸Firstly their products make me nostalgic because the face mask smells like multani mitti which my mom used to apply to my face in my childhood and hair cleanser smells like shikakai - it reminded me of simpler times when such products made my skin clean and hair long and thick. Sorry for the no makeup face - wanted to keep it real and transparent and also for the long videoooo... was keeping it all very raw so kept talking haha. But it’s all worth it ❤️

latestPosts.caption:
Had such a fun day at @ratnadeepforyou when @epigamia.official had their Yogurt Bar setup and I got to try a super yum bowl made with Epigamia Turbo and toppings of my choice - nuts,granola,seed mix!!! 🥣💪 It was a special one day thing and I’m so glad I didn’t miss it!

What I love about the Turbo range is that it’s packed with protein,such an easy and tasty way to help meet your daily intake 🙌 Perfect for a quick snack or post-workout bite!

Ratnadeep is seriously my go-to store as it’s massive, always stocked with the best stuff, and I end up finding something new every time 🛒✨
Can we have more yogurt bars like this, please? 🤤🤤🤤

It was the summer of love 💜
